erty lot lines. Hand colored to emphasize municipal (city/borough/township) boundaries and territories. Prime meridian: New York. Map sheets mounted on cloth backing to form northern/southern segments. LC copy imperfect: Darkened, fold-lined, originally printed in multiple sections (later conjoined), mounted on cloth backing that replaces the original backing, missing small sections at edges and at internal fold lines. Includes 11 town/village insets (including New Brunswick, Perth Amboy, South Amboy), local business directories, distance table, and illustrations of prominent buildings. LC Land ownership maps, 457 Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image. 2 copies"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:39:18.487Z", "group": ["gmd.mar", "catalog-split-10", "catalog", "general-maps", "main-catalog-split-10"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2012593677/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/gmd/gmd381/g3813/g3813m/la000457.gif", "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/gmd/gmd381/g3813/g3813m/la000457.gif#h=155&w=150", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmd381:g3813:g3813m:la000457/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=2303&w=2233", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmd381:g3813:g3813m:la000457/full/pct:25/0/default.jpg#h=4607&w=4466"], "index": 8, "language": ["english"], "location": ["middlesex county", "united states", "new jersey", "south amboy", "perth amboy", "new brunswick"], "mime_type": ["image/gif", "image/tiff", "image/jpeg", "image/jp2"], "number": ["2012593677", "2014-07-09t12:24:15", "2025-06-07t06:10:59.800000", "sheet"], "online_format": ["image"], "original_format": ["map"], "partof": ["cultural landscapes", "county landownership maps", "catalog", "geography and map division"], "score": 57.0591, "shelf_id": "G3813.M5 1861 .W3 G3813.M5 1861 .W3 Copy 2", "site": ["catalog"], "subject": ["landowners", "perth amboy (n.j.)",